        "src": "__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2021/07/Amish-Buggy-Turned-Into-Roaring-Hotrod--3.jpg",
        "width": 1920,
        "height": 1080,
        "caption": "photo credit: The Daily Record"
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Before you think building such a thing is a good idea, even Mellott admits his build isn’t exactly safe. After all, the buggy was constructed using very old technology and flimsy materials, It wasn’t made to sustain a crash at high speeds. Still, Mellott sometimes takes the hot rod on the highway and pushes it to 65, we imagine because he just likes the thrill.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
